index_terms: CHICAGO MILWAUKEE ST. PAUL PACIFIC RAILROAD
references: Related: CF 256355, Ord 14532, Ord 52460, Ord 67088, Ord 75743
summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the franchise of the Chicago, Milwaukee and St. Paul Railway Company of Washington granted by Ordinance 14532, as amended, amending Sections 1 and 3 thereof to extend the term thereof to December 31, 1968, subject to termination by the City after December 31, 1967, and providing for an acceptance.
